<% provide(:title, 'Interest Rates') %>

<div id="slide">
  <h2>What will Interest Rates COST you?</h2>

  <p>
    Honestly, we here at Fiscal Fitness don't think we can make you a millionaire. We can, however, give you the knowledge to defend yourself against predatory leanders and stop making the rich richer.
  </p>

  <p>
    Let's take a looks at some common interest rate expenses you are likely to pay in your life. Notice, how these rates are all higher than the interest rates an indivdual is expected to earn.
  </p>

  <p>
    Test out the following input Interest Rates:
  </p>

  <table class="approx_irates">
    <tr>
      <th>Mortgage</th>
      <th>Auto Loans</th>
      <th>Student Loans</th>
      <th>Credit Card Debt</th>
      <th>Question 1</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>4.39%</td>
      <td>3.00%</td>
      <td>3.90%</td>
      <td>14.95%</td>
      <td>25%</td>
    </tr>
  </table>


  <div class="cost" id="irate_form">
    <form  method=post id="iRateForm">
    <table>
      <tr>
        <td>Monthly Investments:</td>
        <td><input class="required" id="pmt" type=number size=13 maxlength=13></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Length of Monthly Investments:</td>
        <td><input class="required" id="numOfPeriods" type=number size=6 maxlength=3>
          <select id="yearOrMonth" size=1>
            <option value="y">Years
            <option value="m">Months
          </select>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Interest Rate:</td>
        <td><input class="required" type=number id="interest" size=6 maxlength=5><b> %</b></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="center" colspan = "2">
          <button class="button bad" id="howMuch">
            How much do Interest Rates Cost?
          </button>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Total Cost with Interest:</td>
        <td>
          <input id="totalInterest" type=text name=total value="0.00" size=20>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Total Cost with out Interest:</td>
        <td>
          <input id="totalNoInterest" type=text name=total value="0.00" size=20>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Extra Expense:</td>
        <td>
          <input id="difference" type=text name=total value="0.00" size=20>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    </form>
  </div>

  <div id="chart_container">
    <%= render 'shared/default_graph' %>
    <div id="legend" class="rickshaw_legend">
      <ul><li class="line"><div class="swatch" style="background-color: rgb(173, 216, 230);"></div><span class="label">Expense with Interest</span></li><li class="line"><div class="swatch" style="background-color: rgb(70, 130, 180);"></div><span class="label">Expense Without Interest</span></li></ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom_left">
    <%= link_to "Back", slide7_path, class: "button" %>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom_right">
    <%= link_to "Next", slide9_path, class: "button" %>
  </div>
</div>

